---

---

<!-- SPACING: Section vertical padding -->
<section id="love-story" class="py-24 px-6 bg-cream overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <!-- SPACING: Header bottom margin -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
            <h2
                class="text-gold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[10px] lg:text-xs font-bold mb-4"
            >
                Our Journey
            </h2>
            <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-serif text-charcoal italic">
                Kisah Cinta Kami
            </h3>
        </div>

        <!-- Story Timeline -->
        <!-- SPACING: Timeline items vertical gap -->
        <div class="space-y-12 relative">
            <!-- Vertical Line Decoration -->
            <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gold/20 -translate-x-1/2 hidden lg:block"
            >
            </div>

            <!-- Milestone 1 -->
            <div
                class="reveal relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 group"
            >
                <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-[45%]"></div>
                <!-- Timeline Dot -->
                <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cream border-2 border-gold flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 shrink-0 shadow-lg"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gold text-sm"
                        >favorite</span
                    >
                </div>
                <!-- SPACING: Card padding and width -->
                <div
                    class="w-full lg:w-[45%] bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-32 border border-white/20 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/20"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-gold font-serif italic text-lg lg:text-xl block mb-2"
                        >Awal Pertemu</span
                    >
                    <h4
                        class="text-charcoal font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
                    >
                        Mei 2022
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-charcoal/70 text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
                        "Pertemuan pertama yang tak terduga, di mana pandangan
                        pertama menjadi awal dari segalanya. Berawal dari
                        komunikasi yang sederhana hingga tumbuh rasa nyaman."
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Milestone 2 -->
            <div
                class="reveal relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center justify-between gap-8 group"
            >
                <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-[45%]"></div>
                <!-- Timeline Dot -->
                <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cream border-2 border-gold flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 shrink-0 shadow-lg"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gold text-sm"
                        >ring_volume</span
                    >
                </div>
                <!-- SPACING: Card padding and width -->
                <div
                    class="w-full lg:w-[45%] bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-32 border border-white/20 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/20"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-gold font-serif italic text-lg lg:text-xl block mb-2"
                        >Lamaran</span
                    >
                    <h4
                        class="text-charcoal font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
                    >
                        Agustus 2025
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-charcoal/70 text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
                        "Dengan niat yang suci, kami memutuskan untuk melangkah
                        ke jenjang yang lebih serius. Momen di mana keluarga
                        dipertemukan untuk menyatukan dua hati."
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Milestone 3 -->
            <div
                class="reveal relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 group"
            >
                <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-[45%]"></div>
                <!-- Timeline Dot -->
                <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold border-2 border-gold flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 shrink-0 shadow-lg"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-cream text-sm"
                        >celebration</span
                    >
                </div>
                <!-- SPACING: Card padding and width -->
                <div
                    class="w-full lg:w-[45%] bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-32 border border-white/20 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/20"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-gold font-serif italic text-lg lg:text-xl block mb-2"
                        >Pernikahan</span
                    >
                    <h4
                        class="text-charcoal font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
                    >
                        Maret 2026
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-charcoal/70 text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
                        "Hari yang dinanti pun tiba. Perjalanan baru dimulai
                        dengan janji suci di hadapan Allah. Puncak dari doa dan
                        penantian kami bersama."
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .rounded-32 {
        border-radius: 32px;
    }
</style>
